You can use a hashmap for this logic.
Use date as key and amount as value.

    HashMap&lt;String, Double&gt; paymentMap = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();
    if (paymentMap.contains(date)) {
        paymentMap.put(date, amount + paymentMap.get(date));
    }
    else {
